<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Plaquette — {{ page.deceasedFullName }}</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .print-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
      background: white;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    }

    .print-actions h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: #1B2B4B; }
    .print-actions p  { font-size: .8rem; color: #6B7280; margin-top: 2px; }

    .btn-print {
      background: #1B2B4B; color: white; border: none;
      padding: .6rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: .9rem;
      cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
    }
    .btn-print:hover { background: #C9A84C; }
    .btn-back { color: #6B7280; text-decoration: none; font-size: .875rem; }

    /* ========================
       PLAQUETTE STYLE 1 — Sobre élégante (noir)
       ======================== */
    .plaque {
      width: 120mm;
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid #1B2B4B;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20mm 15mm;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .plaque--dark {
      background: #1B2B4B;
      border-color: #C9A84C;
    }

    .plaque--marble {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f8f8 0%, #e8e8e8 50%, #f8f8f8 100%);
      border-color: #888;
    }

    /* Flamme décorative */
    .plaque__flame {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
      display: block;
      opacity: .7;
    }

    .plaque__name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 20pt;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #1B2B4B;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .plaque--dark .plaque__name { color: #C9A84C; }
    .plaque--marble .plaque__name { color: #333; }

    .plaque__dates {
      font-family: 'Cormorant', serif;
      font-size: 13pt;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #555;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }

    .plaque--dark .plaque__dates { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }

    .plaque__divider {
      width: 40mm;
      height: 1px;
      background: #C9A84C;
      margin: 0 auto 8mm;
    }

    .plaque--marble .plaque__divider { background: #888; }

    /* QR Code */
    .plaque__qr {
      width: 30mm;
      height: 30mm;
      margin: 0 auto 5mm;
      display: block;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2mm;
      background: white;
    }

    .plaque__scan-text {
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: #888;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 3mm;
    }

    .plaque--dark .plaque__scan-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); }

    .plaque__code {
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #aaa;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .plaque--dark .plaque__code { color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); }

    /* ========================
       SECTION STYLES
       ======================== */
    .styles-section {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .style-label {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: #6B7280;
      margin-top: .75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ========================
       PRINT
       ======================== */
    @media print {
      body { background: white; padding: 0; }
      .print-actions { display: none; }
      .styles-section { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0; }

      .plaque {
        box-shadow: none;
        page-break-after: always;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .style-label { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  {# Barre d'actions (masquée à l'impression) #}
  <div class="print-actions">
    <div>
      <h2>Plaquette mémorielle — {{ page.deceasedFullName }}</h2>
      <p>Choisissez un style et imprimez. Le SVG est disponible pour la gravure laser.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="{{ path('app_qrcode_show', {slug: page.slug}) }}" class="btn-back">← Retour</a>
    <button class="btn-print" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Imprimer / Enregistrer PDF</button>
  </div>

  {# 3 styles de plaquettes #}
  <div class="styles-section">

    {# Style 1 : Blanc sobre #}
    <div>
      <div class="plaque">
        <span class="plaque__flame">🕯️</span>
        <div class="plaque__name">{{ page.deceasedFirstName }}<br>{{ page.deceasedLastName }}</div>
        <div class="plaque__dates">{{ plaque.birth_year }} — {{ plaque.death_year }}</div>
        <div class="plaque__divider"></div>
        <img src="{{ plaque.qr_url }}" alt="QR Code" class="plaque__qr">
        <div class="plaque__scan-text">Scannez pour rendre hommage</div>
        <div class="plaque__code">{{ page.pageCode }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-label">Style 1 — Blanc sobre</div>
    </div>

    {# Style 2 : Marine doré #}
    <div>
      <div class="plaque plaque--dark">
        <span class="plaque__flame">🕯️</span>
        <div class="plaque__name">{{ page.deceasedFirstName }}<br>{{ page.deceasedLastName }}</div>
        <div class="plaque__dates">{{ plaque.birth_year }} — {{ plaque.death_year }}</div>
        <div class="plaque__divider"></div>
        <img src="{{ plaque.qr_url }}" alt="QR Code" class="plaque__qr">
        <div class="plaque__scan-text">Scannez pour rendre hommage</div>
        <div class="plaque__code">{{ page.pageCode }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-label">Style 2 — Marine & doré</div>
    </div>

    {# Style 3 : Marbre #}
    <div>
      <div class="plaque plaque--marble">
        <span class="plaque__flame">✦</span>
        <div class="plaque__name">{{ page.deceasedFirstName }}<br>{{ page.deceasedLastName }}</div>
        <div class="plaque__dates">{{ plaque.birth_year }} — {{ plaque.death_year }}</div>
        <div class="plaque__divider"></div>
        <img src="{{ plaque.qr_url }}" alt="QR Code" class="plaque__qr">
        <div class="plaque__scan-text">Scannez pour rendre hommage</div>
        <div class="plaque__code">{{ page.pageCode }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="style-label">Style 3 — Marbre</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  {# Instructions gravure #}
  <div style="max-width:700px;background:white;border-radius:12px;padding:1.5rem;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.06);">
    <h3 style="font-size:1rem;color:#1B2B4B;margin-bottom:1rem;">📐 Instructions pour gravure laser</h3>
    <ol style="font-size:.875rem;color:#6B7280;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.25rem;">
      <li>Téléchargez le <a href="{{ path('app_qrcode_download_svg', {slug: page.slug}) }}" style="color:#1B2B4B;font-weight:600;">fichier SVG haute résolution</a> (vectoriel, pas de pixelisation)</li>
      <li>Transmettez le fichier à votre graveur avec les dimensions souhaitées (recommandé : 60×60 mm minimum)</li>
      <li>Précisez une correction d'erreur <strong>ECC H</strong> (le QR Code fonctionne même partiellement endommagé)</li>
      <li>Testez le QR Code gravé avec votre smartphone avant installation définitive</li>
      <li>Le QR Code pointe vers : <code style="background:#F4F6F9;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-size:.8rem;">{{ plaque.memorial_url }}</code></li>
    </ol>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
